      "content": "# createMockAdapter\n\n`createMockAdapter()` returns a pure-JavaScript `VGPUAdapter`. Its devices allocate\nin-memory buffers backed by `Uint8Array`, making core testable without Dawn or native\nGPU libraries.\n"
